== /furnace ==

=== Basics ===

//Remotely manages a furnace you set.//

**Usage:** /furnace [set/show]

**Permission Nodes**
 * rcmds.furnace

=== In Depth ===

{{{/furnace}}} allows for a particular furnace to be selected and opened at any time. For a furnace to be selected, the
sender must look at it and use {{{/furnace set}}}. The furnace can then be opened using {{{/furnace show}}} and
manipulated.

=== Examples ===

{{{/furnace set}}} - Set a furnace.\\
{{{/furnace show}}} - Show the furnace that was set.